      "span_text": "The natural history, pathogenesis, host susceptibility factors, virulence, viral kinetics, period of greatest infectiousness, underlying mechanisms of protective immunity, and factors governing treatment outcome are also unknown.  This lack of knowledge is hindering the development of drug treatment, adjunctive treatments, specifi c diagnostic tests, biomarkers, and vaccines."
